    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience just how quickly things can change as an unsuspecting high schooler who suddenly becomes the center of a government program. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll need to utilize your closest friendships and all of your willpower if you want to leave in one piece.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you handle the pressure, or will you unravel at the seams? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >EXODUS: Sunflower on the Horizon is a deeply compelling, original anime-style RPG. The game is reminiscent of both visual novels and RPGs- Taking with it only the best of what both experiences offer, and combining to create a unique and inventive take on a classic genre.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354460/extras/91df0d3865dea309a9705d6f65ddcf5d.poster.avif?t=1765016733\" width=800 height=606 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354460/extras/91df0d3865dea309a9705d6f65ddcf5d.webm?t=1765016733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354460/extras/91df0d3865dea309a9705d6f65ddcf5d.mp4?t=1765016733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                 <u><strong>FEATURES</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thought-provoking sci-fi narrative</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense, challenging turn-b